            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>Io</abbr><ex>vi</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>S</abbr><ex>oli</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Invi</abbr><ex>cto</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>Deo Genitori <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>r</abbr><ex>upe</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>n</abbr><ex>ato</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Aeli</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> Hylas XX <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibertus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pr</abbr><ex>o</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>sa</abbr><ex>lute</ex></expan> et Horientis <note>sic</note> <expan><abbr>fil</abbr><ex>i</ex></expan> sui et Apuleia eius <expan><abbr>sig</abbr><ex>num</ex></expan> numinis cum absidata <lb n="2"/>ex voto <expan><abbr>pos</abbr><ex>uit</ex></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Ursprüngliche Herkunft aus Apulum oder Sarmizegetusa unklar (vgl. IDR).</p>
